name: The Sophisticate - Card Case Wallet - Wickett & Craig
description:
The Sophisticate is an upscale take on our original Slim1 card case. For this version of The Sophisticate, we use our premium Wickett & Craig English Bridle leather. This leather is firm, yet supple. Like our Horween version of this card case, it isn't dainty. This leather is the same thickness that we use for many of our belts. It will soften with time, but it'll maintain its durability.

Precise clean cuts, minimal stitching, rich colors, and a luxurious hand ensure you'll be reaching for this card case even if you don't need to remove any of its contents.

- Wickett & Craig English Bridle leather
- 'Dark Chocolate' Irish linen thread
- Hand dyed & burnished edges
- Will hold 3 cards in the front pocket and up to 5 or 6 cards in the center pocket

name: The Sophisticate - Card Case Wallet - Horween
description:

name: The Catcher 2.0 - Handmade Leather Camera Wrist Strap - Red
description:
The Catcher has been updated to version 2.0!

We start with Horween's beautifully pebbled 'football' leather and then back it with soft red suede for added comfort. The rest of the strap is made with premium thick natural veg-tanned leather for strength. There is minimal stitching to maintain the integrity of the leather, but where it is stitched, it is extremely durable thanks to the Irish linen thread.

This strap will look great while keeping your camera securely affixed to your wrist.

Also available with chocolate suede for a more low-key look, check our other listing for this option.

- Horween 'football' leather wrist pad
- Hefty veg-tan strap for security
- Irish linen hand-stitching
- Soft suede for added comfort
- US Made heavy duty split rings for connecting the strap to your camera's lugs

name: The Minimalist - Camera Wrist Strap - Natural
description:
Clean, simple lines, and unobtrusive styling are the key points of The Minimalist camera wrist strap. The natural tan veg-tan leather used for this strap is a hearty 7ozs (approximate weight), which means it is more than strong enough for your point & shoot, M4/3, or small DSLR camera. This leather will develop a rich caramelly patina and soft hand with use. 

Security of your camera when attached to this strap is key, which is why we also use 200 lb tensile strength coated Kevlar cord to secure the strap to your camera's lugs.

- Natural Veg-tan leather
- Black coated Kevlar attachment cord
- Brass Chicago Screws

name: Three Bow Ties & Onesie Set, Dapper and Preppy Baby Boy Outfit, Baby Blue Collection
description:
Three bow ties and a super soft onesie for your Little Man. Bow ties attach to onesie with snaps so that they are safe for use on babies and easy to remove so that the onesie may be washed.

This particular set "Baby Blue" includes the following bow ties: Grandpa Blue, Lemon Yellow, and Stormy Blue. We have other sets available featuring different combinations of bow tie colors/patterns and a "choose your own" option available too. 

Bow ties are hand made in our workshop in Atlanta, Georgia. 

The onesies are luxuriously soft and tag-less for optimal comfort! Available in sizes 0-3 months, 3-6 months, 6-12 months, and 12-18 months.
